Introduction

Minhee is a South Korean singer. She was a member and the lead vocalist of the girl group Stellar until their disbandment. Minhee along with Hyoeun, joined the group on January 27, 2012. On February 8, the digital song "UFO" marked their formal debut on the group.

Stellar revealed during a fan meetup on February 25, 2018, that the band was splitting up after seven years.
